other_tests.findings: Fibroblast cultures showed normal binding of iodinated IGF-I, but autophosphorylation and activation of downstream signaling upon challenging with IGF-I were markedly reduced.

other_tests.changes_over_time: In 1981, an exercise test showed a peak GH concentration of 109 mU/liter.

other_tests.findings: Spontaneous GH secretion showed low levels (3.4 mU/liter).
